trends: There has been one other sighting in Bangkok
There were no other sightings in Bangkok on or around June 24th 2006
divs: Sighting DetailsI was in Thailand having fried grasshopper dipped in chocolate. And then the wings went in my nose and I started sneezing.So when I sneezed i looked up at the sky and there is was a Boomerrang Shaped flying object flaying really fast in an angle. And I thought I was high from the Grasshopper then the object came down behind the trees of the park and I saw an alien come out of the ship looking at me. And sending messages to my head that I could not understand. Then I blacked out.
